<p class="">I am not able to give the terms of the reply, which was of a confidential character. I may, however, say that the Czechoslovak Government welcomed the interest shown by the British and French Governments in the question at issue, and gave assurances of their intention to endeavour to reach a just and equitable settlement.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
